{"type": "article", "id": 48739, "title": "下一个十年，兰蔻继续创新发力", "description": "", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 269276, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "<p>没有疲软的市场，只有疲软的产品。在几近饱和的高端护肤品市场分得一杯羹已是不易之事，如何继续为一款已经“火了十年”的系列产品打造出一片立足之地，小黑瓶的下一个十年已经开启。</p><p>从爆款单品，到销量王牌。从肌底液传奇，到小黑瓶安瓶的传奇再现。<b><a href=\"http://e.cn.miaozhen.com/r/k=2068220&amp;p=7C0pu&amp;dx=__IPDX__&amp;rt=2&amp;ns=__IP__&amp;ni=__IESID__&amp;v=__LOC__&amp;xa=__ADPLATFORM__&amp;tr=__REQUESTID__&amp;ro=sm&amp;o=http://www.lancome.com.cn/landing/cny17.html?&amp;utm_source=Qdaily&amp;utm_medium=NVD_DISP&amp;utm_content=02-07Qdaily_6thfeeds_CreativeA&amp;utm_campaign=CN_20171227_GEN_CNY_LPD_LAN_FS_Regular_NVD_DISP_MO\" rel=\"nofollow\">「小黑瓶」鸿运开年新年限量版的上市</a></b>与<b>「小黑瓶」肌底精华浸润修护面膜更新</b>，某种程度上可以看作是在预告2018年兰蔻的在这一明星护肤系列的新动作——通过推出符合时节热点的限量版礼盒，在带动产品附加价值销售的同时，进而提升品牌高端精致的价值感。另一方面，不断更新技术，紧跟市场发展的脚步，升级稳固的产品线。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712291609244uXgTZCL79zdIGKx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668056\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018年「小黑瓶」肌底精华浸润修护面膜更新</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171229160931fT2eDrP3Qw7sd6xO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.179167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018年「小黑瓶」肌底精华浸润修护面膜更新</div></figcaption></figure><figcaption class=\"images-name\">2018年「小黑瓶」肌底精华浸润修护面膜更新</figcaption></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171229154622V3EKMjNeP8ytdpnR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672222\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171229154634F936djOfZuCBKqw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.024960\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171229154640uatQHRdjXhq7F6TE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.959707\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b>2018「小黑瓶」鸿运限量版首发（<a href=\"http://e.cn.miaozhen.com/r/k=2068220&amp;p=7C0pu&amp;dx=__IPDX__&amp;rt=2&amp;ns=__IP__&amp;ni=__IESID__&amp;v=__LOC__&amp;xa=__ADPLATFORM__&amp;tr=__REQUESTID__&amp;ro=sm&amp;o=http://www.lancome.com.cn/landing/cny17.html?&amp;utm_source=Qdaily&amp;utm_medium=NVD_DISP&amp;utm_content=02-07Qdaily_6thfeeds_CreativeA&amp;utm_campaign=CN_20171227_GEN_CNY_LPD_LAN_FS_Regular_NVD_DISP_MO\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击购买</a>）</b><br></p><p>不做“红极一时”的爆款、也不做“碌碌无为”的经典，兰蔻小黑瓶十周年的星路历程，是否也曾经或将要与你一同开启美好未来？不管时代如何改变，时间是检验产品和品牌的最好标准。下一个十年，兰蔻已经做好了准备，来接受你的检验。</p>"}